    "description": "Are you a skilled Property Consultant looking for your next big career move? Sunteck Realty Asia Pacific Associates in Dhanbad offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Sunteck Realty Asia Pacific Associates:\nSunteck Realty Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sunteck Realty Asia Pacific Associates!",
